# sparrow-static-analysis tools: commit the .NET machinery (csproj/.cs) and explicit small
# fixture .xls files under references/triage/e2e-lab; never commit build outputs,
# ad-hoc/generated fixture .xls files, or the tool's split output dirs.
skills/sparrow-static-analysis/tools/**/bin/
skills/sparrow-static-analysis/tools/**/obj/
# publish\ = 폐쇄망 반입용 self-contained/framework-dependent 발행 산출물(publish-airgap.ps1). 머신마다 생성, 커밋 금지.
skills/sparrow-static-analysis/tools/**/publish/
*.items/
fixture.xls

